{"analytics_identifier":"EA42","base_path":"/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory","content_id":"43b6c342-c6b7-4ef1-93d2-98f0a9130ccc","description":"The Defence Science and Technology Laboratory (Dstl) brings mission success to UK defence and security through science and technology advantage. Dstl is an executive agency, sponsored by the Ministry of Defence .","details":{"acronym":"Dstl","alternative_format_contact_email":"centralenquiries@dstl.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Defence Science and Technology Laboratory (Dstl) brings mission success to UK defence and security through science and technology advantage.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Defence Science and Technology Laboratory\">Dstl</abbr> is an executive agency, sponsored by the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence\">Ministry of Defence</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"ministry-of-defence","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67910211cf977e4bf9a2f176/s960_Dstl_delivering_mission_success_960x640.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67910211b1e4f5cbd3a34ded/s300_Dstl_delivering_mission_success_960x640.png"},"foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"Defence Science and Technology Laboratory","image":{"alt_text":"Defence Science and Technology Laboratory","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6791021120bce57216a2f17a/Dstl_delivering_mission_success_960x640.png"}},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory/about/accessible-documents-policy","title":"Accessible documents policy"},{"href":"/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory/about/equality-and-diversity","title":"Equality and diversity"},{"href":"/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory/about/media-enquiries","title":"Media enquiries"},{"href":"/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory/about/our-governance","title":"Our governance"},{"href":"/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory/about/recruitment","title":"Working for Dstl"},{"href":"https://www.civilservicejobs.service.gov.uk/csr/jobs.cgi?pageaction=searchbyquick&storesearchcontext=1&nghr_dept=183873","title":"Jobs"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/dstl-develops-first-smart-find-and-strike-system-for-faster-battlefield-decisions","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69fb3114cd2e0e8b5b20b19a/s712_AIM_user_interface_Credit_INVERGEX_960x640.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69fb31142a6137e93226b7bf/s465_AIM_user_interface_Credit_INVERGEX_960x640.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69fb3114cd2e0e8b5b20b199/AIM_user_interface_Credit_INVERGEX_960x640.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-05-05T14:06:06.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Commanders will better coordinate surveillance, targeting and weapons across platforms and uncrewed systems.</p>\n</div>","title":"Dstl develops first smart ‘find and strike’ system for faster battlefield decisions"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/dstl-assesses-robotic-systems-in-hazardous-incident-recovery-trial","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e0a4fc6c6ccf244be42e1b/s712_DSTL-O-NTAGTrial-960x640.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e0a4fc6c6ccf244be42e1c/s465_DSTL-O-NTAGTrial-960x640.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e0a4fc6c6ccf244be42e1a/DSTL-O-NTAGTrial-960x640.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-16T09:52:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Robots, not people, could respond to future high-risk incidents following the Defence Science and Technology Laboratory’s recent testing.</p>\n</div>","title":"Dstl assesses robotic systems in hazardous incident recovery trial"},{"document_type":"Case Study","href":"/government/case-studies/ensuring-the-future-of-uk-radar-measurement-capability","image":{"alt_text":"Large pit with a dirt track and yellow painted circle at the front and white building towards the back","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e1f1c220b52e4144868984/s712_Radar_Measurement_-_DotGov_Export_72dpi.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e1f1c261d2e8e9b9e42eb7/s465_Radar_Measurement_-_DotGov_Export_72dpi.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69e1f1c26c6ccf244be42ee3/Radar_Measurement_-_DotGov_Export_72dpi.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-14T08:59:29.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Knowing how easily our platforms can be detected by radar is vital for keeping them safe and spotting any weaknesses.</p>\n</div>","title":"Ensuring the future of UK radar measurement capability"},{"document_type":"Case Study","href":"/government/case-studies/salisbury-nerve-agent-attack-2018-dstl-impact","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69f0674e606c20d412163496/s712_Lab-960x640.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69f0674eb7ee6e0fb30a1325/s465_Lab-960x640.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69f0674ed73531b6720a1312/Lab-960x640.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-12-04T13:59:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Find out more about Dstl’s central role in the response to the nerve agent attack in 2018 - one of the most serious criminal and international incidents in recent years.</p>\n</div>","title":"Salisbury nerve agent attack 2018: Dstl impact"},{"document_type":"Detailed guide","href":"/guidance/access-dstls-published-research","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6888e0576478525675738f82/s712_AHQCPL13-OFFICIAL-20230516-005-149_defence_imagery.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6888e05776f68cc8414d5afe/s465_AHQCPL13-OFFICIAL-20230516-005-149_defence_imagery.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6888e0578b3a37b63e738f85/AHQCPL13-OFFICIAL-20230516-005-149_defence_imagery.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-10T12:30:07.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>View highlights of some of our most recently published research on this page. You can also download a complete list of our published research.</p>\n</div>","title":"Access Dstl's published research"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/drones-using-ai-to-spot-explosive-dangers-and-help-keep-soldiers-safe","image":{"alt_text":"Soldier looking at two screens side by side","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69ce2adceafd66b876458c30/s712_Dstl-O-EOD-Drones-8622_ai_drones_gov.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69ce2adceafd66b876458c2f/s465_Dstl-O-EOD-Drones-8622_ai_drones_gov.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69ce2adc604bb817c3458c33/Dstl-O-EOD-Drones-8622_ai_drones_gov.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-02T09:51:59.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>AI-powered drone technology has been successfully trialled to identify landmines and explosive ordnance.</p>\n</div>","title":"Drones using AI to spot explosive dangers and help keep soldiers safe"}],"ordered_featured_links":[{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory/about","title":"About Dstl"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/dstls-areas-of-work-programmes-and-project-portfolios","title":"What we do: our work and facilities"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/how-to-sell-to-dstl-industry-academia-and-other-research-organisations","title":"Suppliers: how to work with us"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/access-dstls-published-research","title":"Access our research "},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory/about/recruitment","title":"Working for us"}],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"service","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"executive_agency","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[{"href":"https://x.com/dstlmod","service_type":"twitter","title":"Twitter"},{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/user/DstlMOD","service_type":"youtube","title":"YouTube"},{"href":"https://www.linkedin.com/company/dstl","service_type":"linkedin","title":"LinkedIn"}]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2012-01-10T15:31:30+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"EA42","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory","base_path":"/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory","content_id":"43b6c342-c6b7-4ef1-93d2-98f0a9130ccc","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-02-12T14:19:29Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Defence Science and Technology Laboratory","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/defence-science-and-technology-laboratory","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_board_members":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/adrian-belton","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/adrian-belton","base_path":"/government/people/adrian-belton","content_id":"70987053-5092-4194-aa08-ae33a0957827","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Adrian Belton","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5fe0cdd28fa8f56afb2296c4/s465_Adrian_Belton_resized.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"ee10ac48-d9f7-456c-9e78-81b438db8cb7","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":6565,"started_on":"2014-08-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"847526af-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Chair leads the <abbr title=\"Defence Science and Technology Laboratory\">Dstl</abbr> Board. The Board’s role is to support and constructively challenge the <abbr title=\"Defence Science and Technology Laboratory\">Dstl</abbr> executive in the development of business strategies, plans, business cases and targets, and to monitor <abbr title=\"Defence Science and Technology Laboratory\">Dstl</abbr>’s business performance against the approved corporate plan.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2020-12-21T16:33:11Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chair","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2020-12-21T16:32:32Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Adrian Belton - Chairman","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-02-14T15:43:12Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Adrian Belton","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/adrian-belton","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/paul-hollinshead","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/paul-hollinshead","base_path":"/government/people/paul-hollinshead","content_id":"ff9468b3-c123-41f6-b253-a6c4d21424b4","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Dr Paul Hollinshead MBA OBE","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/620a23dbd3bf7f4f02760709/s465_Dr_Paul_Hollinshead_Dstl_960x640.png"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"bb1c41a4-37b1-4eb2-a4f7-ca9daf0c9e4d","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":7552,"started_on":"2022-02-14T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"8475256c-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>With direct line responsibility for members of the Executive team, the CE leads <abbr title=\"Defence Science Technology Laboratory\">Dstl</abbr> as an Executive Agency, delivering value-for-money science and technology-based support and advice to customers. This includes getting the best out of suppliers and partners, and balancing short-term delivery with long-term capability.</p>\n\n<p>The CE role is ultimately responsible for ensuring:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the financial viability of <abbr title=\"Defence Science Technology Laboratory\">Dstl</abbr>\n</li>\n  <li>that customers are satisfied</li>\n  <li>that <abbr title=\"Defence Science Technology Laboratory\">Dstl</abbr>’s staff are suitably engaged and rewarded for their contributions</li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-01-07T13:27:07Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Executive","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-02-14T09:46:00Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Dr Paul Hollinshead MBA OBE - Chief Executive","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-02-14T09:41:47Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Dr Paul Hollinshead MBA OBE","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/paul-hollinshead","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/tim-sheldon","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/tim-sheldon","base_path":"/government/people/tim-sheldon","content_id":"6e00e214-f433-4318-b663-160e348b84e2","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Dr Tim Sheldon","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6671714363178530b7692cb1/s465_Dstl-O-TimSheldon-07.05.24-6615_gov_uk.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"55065a03-93b2-4992-94ad-30639319ad56","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":1,"started_on":"2024-04-15T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"f434f8b6-2190-4f60-b0ea-7d2e0a41efa5","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Delivery Officer (<abbr title=\"Chief Delivery Officer\">CDO</abbr>) is accountable to the <abbr title=\"Defence Science and Technology Laboratory\">Dstl</abbr> Chief Executive for the delivery of the billion-pound science and technology portfolio, delivering an agreed portfolio of work to provide high impact, innovative and cost effective capability solutions in support of defence and security’s highest priority requirements. Heading up the Delivery Directorate, the <abbr title=\"Chief Delivery Officer\">CDO</abbr> ensures the correct triage, planning and prioritisation takes place, engaging with customers and the supply chain to shape and deliver future demand through the most appropriate routes.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-04-15T12:24:37Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Delivery Officer","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-04-15T12:30:43Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Dr Tim Sheldon - Chief Delivery Officer","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-04-15T12:29:14Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Dr Tim Sheldon","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/tim-sheldon","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/rob-cocks","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/rob-cocks","base_path":"/government/people/rob-cocks","content_id":"543d1d0c-9662-4227-ab4d-a5a38eb15066","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Rob Cocks","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67aa274831fb10faa31484b0/s465_Dstl_Rob_Cocks-960x640.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"24a8a506-371b-4890-b6bd-3432888c3ff9","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":1,"started_on":"2025-01-13T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"36cf541d-bd92-41ff-9420-73c2917e0d86","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Finance Officer is responsible for Dstl’s Finance, Strategy and Governance Division.</p>\n\n<p>The purpose of this Division is to manage and oversee all aspects of financial management within Dstl, to develop Dstl’s corporate strategies and plans, to maintain and operate the governance framework within Dstl, including Dstl’s approach to risk management, to oversee Dstl’s corporate performance regime, and to deliver a complete intellectual property management service for Dstl.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2018-07-30T14:51:13Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Finance Officer","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-01-13T12:20:56Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Rob Cocks - Chief Finance Officer","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-01-27T09:24:22Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Rob Cocks","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/rob-cocks","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/simon-donnan","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/simon-donnan","base_path":"/government/people/simon-donnan","content_id":"6205a889-df4d-4ff2-9abc-108f4a3780d1","details":{"image":{"url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/674459e24a89e48361cb353a/s465_DSC_5685.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"960201ad-5a6a-4245-a6ba-074fe9969ee5","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2024-11-25T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"59e79e8e-bdc4-4e9e-9452-16b0392a66a7","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Operating Officer is responsible for leading a range of Dstl’s core business enabling operations which include health, safety and environmental protection, facilities and infrastructure (including the National Biosecurity Centre Programme), technical services, data and digital services, security and resilience.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-02-17T11:46:35Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Operating Officer","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-11-25T11:19:51Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Simon Donnan - Chief Operating Officer","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-02-17T11:43:02Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Simon Donnan","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/simon-donnan","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/teresa-stanley","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/teresa-stanley","base_path":"/government/people/teresa-stanley","content_id":"bd877a8d-c9da-4cd7-8228-7947e89fc111","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Teresa Stanley","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66269c631cbbb3400ba7e605/s465_DSTL-O-Teresa_Stanley-05072023-D2336-078-1_gov_uk.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"e618b64e-ad22-48dd-9fca-9dc3b5403e50","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":1,"started_on":"2023-07-28T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"4ea11c19-d9fb-4cd8-9c8d-7f12d36d43c3","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief People Officer provides strategic ‘people’ advice to underpin strategic aims and policies, and defines leadership and people management required to ensure effective delivery of <abbr title=\"Defence Science and Technology Laboratory\">Dstl</abbr>’s strategic aims.</p>\n\n<p>The Chief People Office leads <abbr title=\"Defence Science and Technology Laboratory\">Dstl</abbr> People, which includes talent acquisition and planning, science and technology careers, employee relations, organisational development, HR business partnering and employee experience. It also includes <abbr title=\"Defence Science and Technology Laboratory\">Dstl</abbr>’s communications function, which enables <abbr title=\"Defence Science and Technology Laboratory\">Dstl</abbr> to create maximum impact through connecting with our key audiences.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-04-22T14:34:16Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief People Officer","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-08-01T10:57:03Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Teresa Stanley - Chief People Officer","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-04-22T14:27:27Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Teresa Stanley","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/teresa-stanley","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/andy-bell","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/andy-bell","base_path":"/government/people/andy-bell","content_id":"8fa2af02-f570-4fff-9848-11db72757109","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Prof Andy Bell","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5c348ea540f0b6446eee6b01/s465_Andy_Bell_gov_uk.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"072fe9d8-c40c-4110-89db-bfd0e37fbbf5","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":5193,"started_on":"2018-10-15T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"f64b6e38-d8e8-4dae-b0f4-f3ea600de1e5","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Science and Technology Officer is responsible for effective leadership of coherent, enterprise-level science and technology portfolio delivery and capability stewardship, through provision of constructive challenge, support and direction to delivery business units.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-12-02T10:33:43Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Science and Technology Officer","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-01-11T14:58:27Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Prof Andy Bell - Chief Technical Officer","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2019-01-08T11:51:01Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Prof Andy Bell","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/andy-bell","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_child_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1064","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/centre-for-defence-enterprise","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/centre-for-defence-enterprise","base_path":"/government/organisations/centre-for-defence-enterprise","content_id":"1ec706bb-34b5-4abd-99c2-f111aa1b46e5","details":{"acronym":"CDE","brand":"ministry-of-defence","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a37db3140f0b649cfaf7c35/s960_DSTL_news.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a37db31ed915d5a62fdc77f/s300_DSTL_news.jpg"},"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Centre for Defence Enterprise"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"replaced","updated_at":null,"url":"http://www.science.mod.uk/engagement/enterprise.aspx"}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Centre for Defence Enterprise","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/centre-for-defence-enterprise","withdrawn":false},{"analytics_identifier":"OT1349","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/